Package com.deloitte.capi.cdm.executioncontrol Description

This package contains POJO objects from the Canonical Data Model for the API, for objects dealing with flow control of the application. These classes are used both for data collection, as well as to drive multithreaded processing, allowing the API to query multiple data sources at once, and amalgamate the results when all have returned.
Author:
David Hunter (Deloitte)
